PN,31001
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778177468
OL,3,CUS and Philippines' biggest-ever
OL,4,Cmilitary drills show China guard is up
OL,6,FThis years' Balikatan military
OL,7,Fexercises were America's opportunity
OL,8,Fto show China it hasn't dropped its
OL,9,Fguard in the Indo-Pacific, and
OL,10,Freassure regional allies that the US
OL,11,Fremains committed to their defence.
OL,13,FIran may be dominating US military
OL,14,Fattention, but this years' joint
OL,15,Fexercises with the Philippines were
OL,16,Fthe biggest yet, rehearsing for a
OL,17,Fconflict that may be still to come.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778177468
OL,3,CUS and Philippines' biggest-ever
OL,4,Cmilitary drills show China guard is up
OL,6,FThe US and the Philippines have been
OL,7,Fstaging Balikatan, which means
OL,8,F''shoulder-to-shoulder'' in Tagalog,
OL,9,Ffor more than 20 years, in which time
OL,10,Fit has gone from being low-key
OL,11,Fsecurity training focused on
OL,12,Fcounterterrorism, to preparing for a
OL,13,Ffull-blown regional conflict.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778177468
OL,3,CUS and Philippines' biggest-ever
OL,4,Cmilitary drills show China guard is up
OL,6,FAnd for the first time this year Japan
OL,7,Fsent combat troops to take part, a
OL,8,Fmove which not only provoked the ire
OL,9,Fof China, but many Japanese people who
OL,10,Ffear the government of Prime Minister
OL,11,FSanae Takaishi is seeking to alter
OL,12,Ftheir post-WWII pacifist constitution.
OL,14,FFor American troops, Balikatan
OL,15,Fprovides a chance to flex some
OL,16,Fmilitary muscle in China's backyard.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778177468
OL,3,CUS and Philippines' biggest-ever
OL,4,Cmilitary drills show China guard is up
OL,6,FIn the event of a war over Taiwan, the
OL,7,FPhilippines could become a major
OL,8,Fstaging ground for the US military, so
OL,9,Fknowing how to operate in a tropical
OL,10,Fenvironment and on an island nation is
OL,11,Fvital for the marine and army
OL,12,Fregiments which would be part of any
OL,13,Fsuch mission.
OL,15,FAt their closest point, the
OL,16,FPhilippines and Taiwan are less than
OL,17,Fsixty miles apart.
OL,19,FOn land, we saw rocket launchers and
OL,20,Ftroops deployed in battle scenarios.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778177468
OL,3,CUS and Philippines' biggest-ever
OL,4,Cmilitary drills show China guard is up
OL,6,FAt sea, the US was joined in a multi-
OL,7,Fnation show of strength, with ships
OL,8,Ffrom Canada, Australia, and Japan.
OL,10,FIn the air, there is clearly one
OL,11,Fdanger dominating modern warfare. We
OL,12,Fwatched a full day of drone target
OL,13,Fpractice.
OL,15,FIt has quickly become a central focus
OL,16,Fof modern military training; unmanned
OL,17,Faerial vehicles (UAV) pose a unique
OL,18,Fthreat that they are still developing
OL,19,Ftechniques to deter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778177468
OL,3,CUS and Philippines' biggest-ever
OL,4,Cmilitary drills show China guard is up
OL,6,FIt took more attempts that I felt
OL,7,Fcomfortable with to shoot down the
OL,8,Fdummy drones.
OL,10,FIf the Chinese were watching, they
OL,11,Fwould have been given the impression
OL,12,Fthat the Americans haven't yet
OL,13,Fperfected their drone marksmanship.
OL,15,FAlthough we were also shown a
OL,16,Fdemonstration of the 'stinger'
OL,17,Fmissile, which in the blink of an eye,
OL,18,Fwas able to seek out and destroy a UAV
OL,19,Ftarget.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778177468
OL,3,CUS and Philippines' biggest-ever
OL,4,Cmilitary drills show China guard is up
OL,6,FThe Chinese government warned the
OL,7,Fnations taking part in these exercises
OL,8,Fthat they were playing with fire,
OL,9,Fdescribing the drills as ''provocative
OL,10,Fand destabilising''.
OL,12,FIt was an accusation we heard Filipino
OL,13,Ffisherman level back at Beijing. Their
OL,14,Fcatch, and therefore their
OL,15,Flivelihoods, have diminished as
OL,16,Ftensions have risen in the South China
OL,17,FSea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778177468
OL,3,CUS and Philippines' biggest-ever
OL,4,Cmilitary drills show China guard is up
OL,6,FIn recent years the Chinese coastguard
OL,7,Fhas been asserting China's expanding
OL,8,Fterritorial claims, firing water
OL,9,Fcannon on fishermen whose families
OL,10,Fhave worked in, what they prefer to
OL,11,Fcall, the West Philippines sea for
OL,12,Fdecades.
OL,14,FSatellite images show that in the last
OL,15,Ftwelve months a new Chinese military
OL,16,Foutpost has been built on the
OL,17,Fpreviously submerged Antelope reef.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778177468
OL,3,CUS and Philippines' biggest-ever
OL,4,Cmilitary drills show China guard is up
OL,6,FIt's the latest in more than a dozen
OL,7,Freclaimed islands now dotted around
OL,8,Fthe South China Sea, able to house
OL,9,FChinese troops and airstrips.
OL,11,FAlong the coast from the Balikatan
OL,12,Fexercises we went to meet a group from
OL,13,Fthe La Paz Fishing Association.
OL,15,FThey told us it's no longer safe for
OL,16,Fthem to fish in the Bajo de Masinloc
OL,17,Fwhich used to be one of their most
OL,18,Flucrative fishing areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778177468
OL,3,CUS and Philippines' biggest-ever
OL,4,Cmilitary drills show China guard is up
OL,6,FDespite it being within Filipino
OL,7,Fterritory, it is now patrolled by
OL,8,FChinese vessels which intimidate, and
OL,9,Fon occasion have rammed, fishing
OL,10,Fvessels that dared to venture out that
OL,11,Ffar.
OL,13,FOne woman told us she fears one day
OL,14,Fher husband won't come home if he
OL,15,Fstrays into what have become contested
OL,16,Fand dangerous waters.
OL,18,FThere were conflicting feelings about
OL,19,Fthe Balikatan military drills and
OL,20,Fwhether hosting the US makes the
OL,21,FPhilippines a bigger target.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778177468
OL,3,CUS and Philippines' biggest-ever
OL,4,Cmilitary drills show China guard is up
OL,6,FOn the one hand, they were concerned
OL,7,Fby what happened during the US-Iran
OL,8,Fwar, when neighbouring countries
OL,9,Fhosting American bases became a target.
OL,11,FThey all live and work within a few
OL,12,Fmiles of a large army and marine base
OL,13,Fwhere the US maintains a presence.
OL,15,FBut given the increased threat they
OL,16,Ffeel from China, most of those we
OL,17,Fspoke to felt that having the backing
OL,18,Fof the US in the Philippines was an
OL,19,Fimportant deterrent, and a necessary
OL,20,Fpartnership for the Filipino military.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31012
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778177468
OL,3,CUS and Philippines' biggest-ever
OL,4,Cmilitary drills show China guard is up
OL,6,FWith shared concerns over regional
OL,7,Fsecurity, Japan has emerged as one of
OL,8,Fthe Philippines' strongest allies.
OL,10,FThe country was occupied by the
OL,11,FJapanese during WW2, and it was
OL,12,Fsuggested to me that the military
OL,13,Fsupport Japan is giving now, is in
OL,14,Fsome way atoning for what they did
OL,15,Fduring that brutal occupation.
OL,17,FThe Japanese government this week
OL,18,Fsigned another new defence agreement
OL,19,Fwith the Philippines, fast-tracking
OL,20,Fthe delivery of Abukama-class
OL,21,Fdestroyers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31013
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778177468
OL,3,CUS and Philippines' biggest-ever
OL,4,Cmilitary drills show China guard is up
OL,6,FThe increase in Japanese arms sales
OL,7,Fthat have prompted protests on the
OL,8,Fstreets of Tokyo, are being welcomed
OL,9,Fby the Filipinos who feel they need
OL,10,Fall the help they can get.
OL,12,FWith so much of the world on a war
OL,13,Ffooting, peace in the Indo-Pacific can
OL,14,Ffeel fragile.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
